                            | Companies such as SmartUp hope to provide an alternative to this style 
                            | of teaching by providing a format more akin to social networking.  Mr 
                            | Meehan explains the app focuses on the need for investors, start-ups and 
                            | corporations to ﬁnd out and showcase what people actually know. 
                .col-flex.col-flex-25
                    a(href="https://www.ft.com/content/1f3b2402-cb3b-11e5-a8ef-ea66e967dd44", class="cbtn btn-dark") Read more
                    
